items.title: Eigenvectors and Eigenvalues explained visually
items.snippet:
Eigenvalues/vectors are instrumental to understanding electrical circuits, 
mechanical systems, ecology and even Google's PageRank algorithm. Let's see 
if visualization can make these ideas more intuitive. To begin, let v be a vector (
shown as a point) and A be a matrix with columns a 1 and a 2 (shown as arrows).

items.title: Eigenvalues of a matrix - MuPAD
items.snippet:
In MuPAD Notebook only, linalg::eigenvalues(A) returns a list of the eigenvalues 
of the matrix A.
items.htmlSnippet:
In MuPAD Notebook only, linalg::eigenvalues(A) returns a list of the eigenvalues
